# Hard Boiled Eggs

Based on [Kenji](http://web.archive.org/web/20251130144914/https://www.seriouseats.com/the-secrets-to-peeling-hard-boiled-eggs) and [Ethan](https://newsletter.ethanchlebowski.com/p/peeling-eggs-perfectly-every-time) ([archive](http://web.archive.org/web/20251018234116/https://newsletter.ethanchlebowski.com/p/peeling-eggs-perfectly-every-time)). Previously based on [https://downshiftology.com/recipes/perfect-soft-boiled-hard-boiled-eggs](https://downshiftology.com/recipes/perfect-soft-boiled-hard-boiled-eggs) ([archive](http://web.archive.org/web/20251114023532/https://downshiftology.com/recipes/perfect-soft-boiled-hard-boiled-eggs/))

