## Recipe

1. In a deep saucepan, bring water to a rolling boil
1. Gently lower the eggs into the boiling water
1. Cook for ~12 minutes
1. Transfer to an ice bath for 15 minutes
1. Potentially chill overnight in the fridge
1. Gently crack around the widest part, then peel under running water

## Notes

- Great for salads, sandwiches, or with stir fry and rice
